<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>513 Sips | Elevated Mobile Bartending</title>
    <meta name="description" content="513 Sips brings the bar to you. Premium mobile bartending for weddings, corporate events, and private parties in Cincinnati.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        navy: { DEFAULT: '#1a2744', light: '#2a3f5f', dark: '#0f172a' },
                        cream: '#faf8f5',
                        copper: { DEFAULT: '#c9a962', light: '#e0c078' },
                        charcoal: '#2d3748'
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        serif: ['Cormorant Garamond', 'serif'],
                        sans: ['Montserrat', 'sans-serif']
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        :root { --navy: #1a2744; --navy-light: #2a3f5f; --navy-dark: #0f172a; --cream: #faf8f5; --copper: #c9a962; --copper-light: #e0c078; --charcoal: #2d3748; }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; background-color: var(--cream); color: var(--charcoal); overflow-x: hidden; line-height: 1.6; }
        .tubelight-nav { position: fixed; top: 1.5rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); z-index: 1000; background: rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border-radius: 9999px; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.1); transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); }
        .tubelight-nav.scrolled { background: rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.95); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.15); }
        .tubelight-container { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; position: relative; }
        .tubelight-logo { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; margin-right: 1.5rem; }
        .tubelight-logo span { color: var(--copper); }
        .tubelight-links { display: flex; position: relative; gap: 0.25rem; }
        .tubelight-link { padding: 0.6rem 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--charcoal); text-decoration: none; border-radius: 9999px; position: relative; z-index: 2; transition: color 0.3s ease; white-space: nowrap; }
        .tubelight-link:hover, .tubelight-link.active { color: var(--navy); }
        .tubelight-highlight { position: absolute; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.25), rgba(224, 192, 120, 0.15)); border-radius: 9999px; transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); z-index: 1; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3); }
        .mobile-menu-btn { display: none; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0.5rem; color: var(--navy); }
        .hero { position: relative; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark) 0%, var(--navy) 50%, var(--navy-light) 100%); }
        .hero-orb { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(80px); opacity: 0.4; pointer-events: none; }
        .orb-1 { width: 500px; height: 500px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.6), transparent 70%); top: -10%; left: -10%; animation: float-orb 20s infinite ease-in-out; }
        .orb-2 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(224, 192, 120, 0.4), transparent 70%); bottom: 10%; right: -5%; animation: float-orb 15s infinite ease-in-out reverse; }
        .orb-3 { width: 300px; height: 300px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3), transparent 70%); top: 40%; left: 30%; animation: float-orb 18s infinite ease-in-out; animation-delay: -5s; }
        @keyframes float-orb { 0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); } 25% { transform: translate(30px, -30px) scale(1.1); } 50% { transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.95); } 75% { transform: translate(20px, 10px) scale(1.05); } }
        .hero-content { text-align: center; color: white; padding: 0 2rem; max-width: 900px; z-index: 10; position: relative; }
        .hero-subtitle { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--copper-light); margin-bottom: 1rem; opacity: 0; }
        .hero-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; opacity: 0; }
        .hero-title span { color: var(--copper); display: inline-block; }
        .hero-description { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 300; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; opacity: 0; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); }
        .hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; opacity: 0; }
        .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); position: relative; overflow: hidden; border: none; }
        .btn::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: -100%; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent); transition: left 0.5s ease; }
        .btn:hover::before { left: 100%; }
        .btn-primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--copper), var(--copper-light)); color: var(--navy-dark); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.4); }
        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.5); }
        .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: white; border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border-color: white; transform: translateY(-3px); }
        .hero-scroll { position: absolute; bottom: 2rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
        .scroll-indicator { width: 24px; height: 40px; border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); border-radius: 12px; position: relative; }
        .scroll-indicator::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 6px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 4px; height: 8px; background: var(--copper); border-radius: 2px; animation: scroll-bounce 2s infinite; }
        @keyframes scroll-bounce { 0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); opacity: 1; } 50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(12px); opacity: 0.3; } }
        section { padding: 6rem 2rem; position: relative; }
        .container { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
        .section-tag { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--copper); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .section-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .section-subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--charcoal); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; opacity: 0.8; }
        .services { background: white; }
        .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
        .service-card { background: var(--cream); border-radius: 24px; padding: 3rem 2rem; text-align: center; transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); position: relative; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1); }
        .service-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--copper), var(--copper-light)); transform: scaleX(0); transition: transform 0.4s ease; }
        .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.1); border-color: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3); }
        .service-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
        .service-icon { width: 90px; height: 90px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--navy-light)); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--copper); transition: all 0.4s ease; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.2); }
        .service-card:hover .service-icon { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg); background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--copper), var(--copper-light)); color: var(--navy); box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.4); }
        .service-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--navy); }
        .service-description { color: var(--charcoal); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; opacity: 0.8; }
        .about { background: var(--cream); overflow: hidden; }
        .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
        .about-image { position: relative; }
        .about-image-main { border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.2); position: relative; }
        .about-image-main img { width: 100%; height: 500px; object-fit: cover; display: block; transition: transform 0.6s ease; }
        .about-image:hover .about-image-main img { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .about-image-accent { position: absolute; bottom: -30px; right: -30px; width: 200px; height: 200px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--copper), var(--copper-light)); border-radius: 24px; z-index: -1; }
        .about-content { padding: 2rem 0; }
        .about-tag { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--copper); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .about-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.2; }
        .about-text { color: var(--charcoal); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; opacity: 0.85; }
        .about-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3); }
        .stat-item { text-align: center; }
        .stat-number { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--copper); display: block; }
        .stat-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--charcoal); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; opacity: 0.7; }
        .team { background: white; }
        .team-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2.5rem; }
        .team-card { background: var(--cream); border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1); }
        .team-card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.12); }
        .team-image { width: 100%; height: 320px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-light), var(--navy)); position: relative; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--copper); }
        .team-info { padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
        .team-name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .team-role { color: var(--copper); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        .team-bio { color: var(--charcoal); font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; line-height: 1.6; }
        .pricing { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-light) 100%); color: white; }
        .pricing .section-title { color: white; }
        .pricing .section-subtitle { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); }
        .pricing .section-tag { color: var(--copper-light); }
        .pricing-container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
        .pricing-calculator { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-radius: 24px; padding: 2.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2); }
        .pricing-result { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2), rgba(224, 192, 120, 0.1)); border-radius: 24px; padding: 2.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3); text-align: center; position: sticky; top: 120px; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); }
        .form-group input, .form-group select { width: 100%; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2); border-radius: 12px; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); color: white; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--copper); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1); }
        .form-group input::placeholder { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); }
        .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
        .estimate-amount { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--copper); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .estimate-label { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .estimate-details { text-align: left; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .estimate-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .estimate-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; padding-top: 0.75rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2); font-weight: 600; }
        .gallery { background: var(--cream); }
        .gallery-filters { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .gallery-filter { padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; background: white; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2); border-radius: 9999px; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--charcoal); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .gallery-filter:hover, .gallery-filter.active { background: var(--copper); border-color: var(--copper); color: var(--navy); }
        .gallery-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; perspective: 1000px; }
        .flip-card { aspect-ratio: 4/3; cursor: pointer; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
        .flip-card-inner { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); transform-style: preserve-3d; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; }
        .flip-card:hover .flip-card-inner { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
        .flip-card-front, .flip-card-back { position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; backface-visibility: hidden; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; }
        .flip-card-front { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-light), var(--navy)); }
        .flip-card-front img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        .flip-card-back { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--navy-light)); transform: rotateY(180deg); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; color: white; }
        .flip-card-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--copper); }
        .flip-card-category { font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; opacity: 0.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .flip-card-description { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.9; line-height: 1.6; }
        .testimonials { background: white; overflow: hidden; }
        .testimonials-container { position: relative; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .testimonial-slider { position: relative; min-height: 350px; }
        .testimonial-item { position: absolute; width: 100%; opacity: 0; transform: translateX(50px); transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); text-align: center; padding: 2rem; }
        .testimonial-item.active { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        .testimonial-image { width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--copper), var(--copper-light)); padding: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
        .testimonial-image-inner { width: 100%; height: 100%; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--copper); }
        .testimonial-quote { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
        .testimonial-author { font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .testimonial-event { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--copper); }
        .testimonial-nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
        .testimonial-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .testimonial-dot.active { background: var(--copper); transform: scale(1.2); }
        .instagram { background: var(--navy); color: white; padding: 4rem 0; overflow: hidden; }
        .instagram .section-title { color: white; }
        .instagram .section-tag { color: var(--copper-light); }
        .instagram-slider-container { position: relative; width: 100%; overflow: hidden; margin: 3rem 0; }
        .instagram-slider { display: flex; gap: 1rem; animation: slide-infinite 30s linear infinite; width: max-content; }
        .instagram-item { width: 280px; height: 280px; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; flex-shrink: 0; position: relative; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-light), var(--navy)); }
        .instagram-item img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.4s ease; }
        .instagram-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.1); }
        .instagram-overlay { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.8); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; }
        .instagram-item:hover .instagram-overlay { opacity: 1; }
        .instagram-icon { color: white; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        @keyframes slide-infinite { 0% { transform: translateX(0); } 100% { transform: translateX(-50%); } }
        .instagram-cta { text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; }
        .faq { background: white; }
        .faq-container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .faq-item { background: var(--cream); border-radius: 16px; margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .faq-item:hover { border-color: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3); }
        .faq-question { padding: 1.5rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .faq-question:hover { color: var(--copper); }
        .faq-icon { width: 24px; height: 24px; transition: transform 0.3s ease; color: var(--copper); }
        .faq-item.active .faq-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); }
        .faq-answer { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.4s ease; }
        .faq-item.active .faq-answer { max-height: 300px; padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem; }
        .faq-answer p { color: var(--charcoal); opacity: 0.8; line-height: 1.7; }
        .contact { background: var(--cream); }
        .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; }
        .contact-info h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--navy); }
        .contact-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .contact-icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--copper), var(--copper-light)); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.2rem; flex-shrink: 0; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
        .contact-item:hover .contact-icon { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg); }
        .contact-details h4 { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .contact-details p, .contact-details a { color: var(--charcoal); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; opacity: 0.8; }
        .contact-details a:hover { color: var(--copper); }
        .contact-form { background: white; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.1); }
        .contact-form .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .contact-form .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--navy); }
        .contact-form .form-group input, .contact-form .form-group textarea, .contact-form .form-group select { width: 100%; padding: 1rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2); border-radius: 12px; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; background: var(--cream); color: var(--charcoal); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .contact-form .form-group input:focus, .contact-form .form-group textarea:focus, .contact-form .form-group select:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--copper); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1); }
        .contact-form .form-group textarea { min-height: 120px; resize: vertical; }
        .contact-form .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
        .footer { background: var(--navy-dark); color: white; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; }
        .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
        .footer-brand .logo { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: inline-block; text-decoration: none; }
        .footer-brand .logo span { color: var(--copper); }
        .footer-brand p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .fluid-dock { display: flex; gap: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border-radius: 9999px; border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2); width: fit-content; }
        .dock-item { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); position: relative; }
        .dock-item:hover { background: var(--copper); color: var(--navy); transform: scale(1.2) translateY(-5px); }
        .dock-item::before { content: attr(data-label); position: absolute; bottom: -30px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); font-size: 0.7rem; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; white-space: nowrap; color: var(--copper); }
        .dock-item:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
        .footer-column h4 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: white; }
        .footer-links { list-style: none; }
        .footer-links li { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        .footer-links a { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease; display: inline-block; }
        .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--copper); transform: translateX(5px); }
        .footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding-top: 2rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
        .footer-bottom p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .mobile-menu { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.98); z-index: 999; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 2rem; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; }
        .mobile-menu.active { opacity: 1; pointer-events: all; }
        .mobile-menu a { color: white; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; }
        .mobile-menu a:hover { color: var(--copper); }
        .mobile-menu-close { position: absolute; top: 2rem; right: 2rem; background: none; border: none; color: white; font-size: 2rem; cursor: pointer; }
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .about-grid, .contact-grid, .pricing-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
            .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .pricing-result { position: static; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .tubelight-nav { width: calc(100% - 2rem); padding: 0.75rem 1rem; }
            .tubelight-links { display: none; }
            .mobile-menu-btn { display: block; }
            .hero-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .hero-buttons { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
            .btn { width: 100%; max-width: 300px; justify-content: center; }
            .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .about-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
            .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .contact-form { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
            .contact-form .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
            .fluid-dock { margin: 0 auto; }
            .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="tubelight-nav" id="navbar">
        <div class="tubelight-container">
            <a href="#" class="tubelight-logo">513 <span>Sips</span></a>
            <div class="tubelight-links" id="tubelight-links">
                <div class="tubelight-highlight" id="tubelight-highlight"></div>
                <a href="#home" class="tubelight-link active" data-index="0">Home</a>
                <a href="#services" class="tubelight-link" data-index="1">Services</a>
                <a href="#about" class="tubelight-link" data-index="2">Who We Are</a>
                <a href="#team" class="tubelight-link" data-index="3">Bartenders</a>
                <a href="#gallery" class="tubelight-link" data-index="4">Gallery</a>
                <a href="#pricing" class="tubelight-link" data-index="5">Pricing</a>
                <a href="#faq" class="tubelight-link" data-index="6">FAQ</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="tubelight-link" data-index="7">Contact</a>
            </div>
            <button class="mobile-menu-btn" id="mobile-menu-btn">
                <i data-lucide="menu" style="width: 24px; height: 24px;"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobile-menu">
        <button class="mobile-menu-close" id="mobile-menu-close">
            <i data-lucide="x" style="width: 32px; height: 32px;"></i>
        </button>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#about">Who We Are</a>
        <a href="#team">Bartenders</a>
        <a href="#gallery">Gallery</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </div>

    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-orb orb-1"></div>
        <div class="hero-orb orb-2"></div>
        <div class="hero-orb orb-3"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Elevated Mobile Bartending</p>
            <h1 class="hero-title">We Bring the <span>Bar</span> to You</h1>
            <p class="hero-description">Premium craft cocktails and professional bartending services for weddings, corporate events, and private celebrations throughout Cincinnati.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <i data-lucide="calendar" style="width: 18px; height: 18px;"></i>
                    Book Now
                </a>
                <a href="#gallery" class="btn btn-secondary">
                    <i data-lucide="images" style="width: 18px; height: 18px;"></i>
                    View Gallery
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-scroll">
            <span>Scroll</span>
            <div class="scroll-indicator"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services" id="services">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-tag">What We Offer</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">Our Services</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">From intimate gatherings to grand celebrations, we create unforgettable beverage experiences tailored to your event.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i data-lucide="heart" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="service-title">Weddings</h3>
                    <p class="service-description">Make your special day unforgettable with custom cocktail menus, champagne service, and professional bartenders who ensure every toast is perfect.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i data-lucide="building-2" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="service-title">Corporate Events</h3>
                    <p class="service-description">Elevate your company gatherings, holiday parties, and networking events with sophisticated beverage service that impresses clients and colleagues.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i data-lucide="party-popper" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="service-title">Private Parties</h3>
                    <p class="service-description">From birthday celebrations to anniversary parties, we bring the bar experience to your home or venue with personalized service.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-image">
                    <div class="about-image-main">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574096079513-d8259312b785?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="513 Sips Bartending">
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-image-accent"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <p class="about-tag">Our Story</p>
                    <h2 class="about-title">Crafting Memories, One Cocktail at a Time</h2>
                    <p class="about-text">513 Sips was founded with a simple mission: to bring the art of craft cocktails to every celebration. Based in Cincinnati, we combine professional expertise with a passion for hospitality to create memorable experiences.</p>
                    <p class="about-text">Our team of certified bartenders brings creativity, professionalism, and attention to detail to every event. We handle everything from setup to cleanup, so you can focus on enjoying your celebration.</p>
                    <div class="about-stats">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-number">500+</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Events Served</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-number">50+</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Signature Drinks</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Satisfaction</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="team" id="team">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-tag">The Team</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">Meet the Bartenders</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Our talented team of mixologists and bartenders are passionate about creating exceptional experiences.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-image">
                        <i data-lucide="user" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-info">
                        <h3 class="team-name">Alex Thompson</h3>
                        <p class="team-role">Lead Mixologist</p>
                        <p class="team-bio">With 10+ years of experience, Alex crafts signature cocktails that tell a story.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-image">
                        <i data-lucide="user" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-info">
                        <h3 class="team-name">Jordan Lee</h3>
                        <p class="team-role">Event Specialist</p>
                        <p class="team-bio">Jordan ensures every event runs smoothly from setup to last call.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-image">
                        <i data-lucide="user" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-info">
                        <h3 class="team-name">Morgan Chen</h3>
                        <p class="team-role">Creative Director</p>
                        <p class="team-bio">Morgan designs custom menus that perfectly match your event's theme.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing" id="pricing">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-tag">Get an Estimate</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">Pricing Calculator</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Plan your event budget with our interactive pricing tool. Get an instant estimate based on your needs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-container">
                <div class="pricing-calculator">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="event-type">Event Type</label>
                            <select id="event-type">
                                <option value="wedding">Wedding</option>
                                <option value="corporate">Corporate Event</option>
                                <option value="private">Private Party</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="guest-count">Number of Guests</label>
                            <input type="number" id="guest-count" min="10" max="500" value="50">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="hours">Event Duration (Hours)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="hours" min="2" max="12" value="4">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="bartenders">Number of Bartenders</label>
                            <input type="number" id="bartenders" min="1" max="10" value="2">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="service-level">Service Level</label>
                        <select id="service-level">
                            <option value="basic">Basic - Beer & Wine</option>
                            <option value="standard" selected>Standard - Full Bar</option>
                            <option value="premium">Premium - Craft Cocktails</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="pricing-result">
                    <div class="estimate-amount" id="estimate-amount">$850</div>
                    <div class="estimate-label">Estimated Total</div>
                    <div class="estimate-details">
                        <div class="estimate-item">
                            <span>Base Service Fee</span>
                            <span id="base-fee">$400</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="estimate-item">
                            <span>Bartenders (2)</span>
                            <span id="bartender-fee">$300</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="estimate-item">
                            <span>Service Level</span>
                            <span id="service-fee">$150</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="estimate-item">
                            <span>Total Estimate</span>
                            <span id="total-fee">$850</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%;">
                        <i data-lucide="send" style="width: 18px; height: 18px;"></i>
                        Get Detailed Quote
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="gallery" id="gallery">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-tag">Our Work</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">Event Gallery</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Browse through moments we've helped create at weddings, corporate events, and private celebrations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-filters">
                <button class="gallery-filter active" data-filter="all">All</button>
                <button class="gallery-filter" data-filter="wedding">Weddings</button>
                <button class="gallery-filter" data-filter="corporate">Corporate</button>
                <button class="gallery-filter" data-filter="private">Private</button>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-grid">
                <div class="flip-card" data-category="wedding">
                    <div class="flip-card-inner">
                        <div class="flip-card-front">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519741497674-611481863552?w=600&h=450&fit=crop" alt="Wedding Event">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flip-card-back">
                            <h3 class="flip-card-title">Elegant Wedding</h3>
                            <p class="flip-card-category">Wedding</p>
                            <p class="flip-card-description">A beautiful summer wedding with signature cocktails and champagne service.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flip-card" data-category="corporate">
                    <div class="flip-card-inner">
                        <div class="flip-card-front">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540575467063-178a50c2df87?w=600&h=450&fit=crop" alt="Corporate Event">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flip-card-back">
                            <h3 class="flip-card-title">Corporate Gala</h3>
                            <p class="flip-card-category">Corporate</p>
                            <p class="flip-card-description">Annual company celebration with premium bar service for 200 guests.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flip-card" data-category="private">
                    <div class="flip-card-inner">
                        <div class="flip-card-front">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530103862676-de8c9debad1d?w=600&h=450&fit=crop" alt="Private Party">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flip-card-back">
                            <h3 class="flip-card-title">Birthday Celebration</h3>
                            <p class="flip-card-category">Private</p>
                            <p class="flip-card-description">40th birthday bash with custom cocktails and personalized service.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flip-card" data-category="wedding">
                    <div class="flip-card-inner">
                        <div class="flip-card-front">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464366400600-7168b8af9bc3?w=600&h=450&fit=crop" alt="Wedding Reception">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flip-card-back">
                            <h3 class="flip-card-title">Garden Wedding</h3>
                            <p class="flip-card-category">Wedding</p>
                            <p class="flip-card-description">Outdoor ceremony with refreshing summer cocktails and mocktails.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flip-card" data-category="corporate">
                    <div class="flip-card-inner">
                        <div class="flip-card-front">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492684223066-81342ee5ff30?w=600&h=450&fit=crop" alt="Corporate Party">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flip-card-back">
                            <h3 class="flip-card-title">Product Launch</h3>
                            <p class="flip-card-category">Corporate</p>
                            <p class="flip-card-description">Tech company launch event with themed cocktails and professional service.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flip-card" data-category="private">
                    <div class="flip-card-inner">
                        <div class="flip-card-front">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527529482837-4698179dc6ce?w=600&h=450&fit=crop" alt="Private Event">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flip-card-back">
                            <h3 class="flip-card-title">Anniversary Party</h3>
                            <p class="flip-card-category">Private</p>
                            <p class="flip-card-description">25th anniversary celebration with vintage cocktails and elegant presentation.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials" id="testimonials">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-tag">Testimonials</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">What Clients Say</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Don't just take our word for it - hear from the people we've had the pleasure of serving.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonials-container">
                <div class="testimonial-slider">
                    <div class="testimonial-item active" data-index="0">
                        <div class="testimonial-image">
                            <div class="testimonial-image-inner">
                                <i data-lucide="user" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="testimonial-quote">"513 Sips made our wedding day absolutely perfect. The signature cocktails were a huge hit with our guests, and the bartenders were professional and friendly."</p>
                        <p class="testimonial-author">Sarah & Michael Johnson</p>
                        <p class="testimonial-event">Wedding - June 2024</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-item" data-index="1">
                        <div class="testimonial-image">
                            <div class="testimonial-image-inner">
                                <i data-lucide="user" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="testimonial-quote">"Our company holiday party was elevated to the next level thanks to 513 Sips. The craft cocktails were amazing and the service was impeccable."</p>
                        <p class="testimonial-author">David Chen</p>
                        <p class="testimonial-event">Corporate Event - December 2024</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-item" data-index="2">
                        <div class="testimonial-image">
                            <div class="testimonial-image-inner">
                                <i data-lucide="user" style="width: 50px; height: 50px;"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="testimonial-quote">"I hired 513 Sips for my 50th birthday party and couldn't be happier. They took care of everything, allowing me to actually enjoy my own party!"</p>
                        <p class="testimonial-author">Amanda Rodriguez</p>
                        <p class="testimonial-event">Private Party - August 2024</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-nav">
                    <div class="testimonial-dot active" data-index="0"></div>
                    <div class="testimonial-dot" data-index="1"></div>
                    <div class="testimonial-dot" data-index="2"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

