                </div>
                <div class="instagram-item">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560512823-829485b8bf24?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Instagram 4">
                    <div class="instagram-overlay">
                        <i data-lucide="instagram" class="instagram-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="instagram-item">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559526324-4b87b5e36e44?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Instagram 5">
                    <div class="instagram-overlay">
                        <i data-lucide="instagram" class="instagram-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="instagram-item">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544145945-f90425340c7e?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Instagram 6">
                    <div class="instagram-overlay">
                        <i data-lucide="instagram" class="instagram-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="instagram-cta">
            <a href="https://instagram.com/513sips" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">
                <i data-lucide="instagram" style="width: 18px; height: 18px;"></i>
                Follow Us
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq" id="faq">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-tag">Questions</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Find answers to common questions about our mobile bartending services.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-container">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>What areas do you serve?</span>
                        <i data-lucide="plus" class="faq-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We primarily serve the Greater Cincinnati area, including Northern Kentucky and Southeast Indiana. For events outside this area, please contact us for availability and travel fees.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>Do you provide the alcohol?</span>
                        <i data-lucide="plus" class="faq-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Due to Ohio liquor laws, we cannot sell alcohol directly. However, we provide a detailed shopping list based on your selected menu and can assist with delivery coordination for an additional fee.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>How far in advance should I book?</span>
                        <i data-lucide="plus" class="faq-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We recommend booking at least 3-6 months in advance for weddings and large events. For smaller private parties, 4-6 weeks notice is typically sufficient. Last-minute bookings may be accommodated based on availability.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>What's included in your service?</span>
                        <i data-lucide="plus" class="faq-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Our service includes professional bartenders, portable bar setup, all necessary bar tools and equipment, glassware (if requested), mixers and garnishes, ice, and complete cleanup. We handle everything so you can enjoy your event.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>Can we create a custom cocktail menu?</span>
                        <i data-lucide="plus" class="faq-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Absolutely! We love creating custom cocktails that match your event theme or personal preferences. During our consultation, we'll discuss your vision and create signature drinks that will wow your guests.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact" id="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <p class="section-tag">Get In Touch</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">Book Your Event</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Ready to elevate your next event? Let's discuss how we can create the perfect beverage experience for you.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-grid">
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <h3>Let's Connect</h3>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i data-lucide="mail" style="width: 24px; height: 24px;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-details">
                            <h4>Email</h4>
                            <a href="mailto:hello@513sips.com">hello@513sips.com</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i data-lucide="phone" style="width: 24px; height: 24px;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-details">
                            <h4>Phone</h4>
                            <a href="tel:+15135555135">(513) 555-5135</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i data-lucide="map-pin" style="width: 24px; height: 24px;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-details">
                            <h4>Location</h4>
                            <p>Cincinnati, OH<br>Serving Greater Cincinnati Area</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i data-lucide="clock" style="width: 24px; height: 24px;"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-details>
                            <h4>Hours</h4>
                            <p>Available 7 Days a Week<br>By Appointment Only</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-form">
                    <form id="booking-form">
                        <div class="form-row">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="contact-name">Your Name</label>
                                <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="contact-email">Email Address</label>
                                <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="email" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-row">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="contact-phone">Phone Number</label>
                                <input type="tel" id="contact-phone" name="phone">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="contact-date">Event Date</label>
                                <input type="date" id="contact-date" name="date">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="contact-event-type">Event Type</label>
                            <select id="contact-event-type" name="event-type">
                                <option value="">Select Event Type</option>
                                <option value="wedding">Wedding</option>
                                <option value="corporate">Corporate Event</option>
                                <option value="private">Private Party</option>
                                <option value="other">Other</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="contact-message">Tell Us About Your Event</label>
                            <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" placeholder="Number of guests, venue, special requests..."></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%;">
                            <i data-lucide="send" style="width: 18px; height: 18px;"></i>
                            Send Inquiry
                        </button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
